```

And to read it back in, you implement the ``operator&gt;&gt;`` accordingly. 
``` language:c++
std::string tag;
is &gt;&gt; tag; // optionally make sure it is &quot;name:&quot;
is &gt;&gt; value.name;
// ... (The commas might need some fiddling... well you wanted help not a full solution...)
